    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Madam,",
        "I am writing to inform you about my jacket which I left after my recent visit to your cinema.",
        "Here is the some details about my item, it is Gucci's jacket, black in color, made from leather. Also it has white lines on the back with Gucci's brand logo on it.",
        "I do not exactly remember where was my seat cause I did not manage to find my ticket but I am sure that it was between really close to emergency exit on the left side of the stage.",
        "I would be grateful if you can check with venue cleaning personnel if they found it and if the answer is positive I could come and pick it up at some point this week.",
        "Thank you in advance and I am looking forward to hearing from you back.",
        "Yours Faithfully,",
        "Sattor Kadirov"
    ],
